{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-2","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor kombinovanih krajeva i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Blendski završetak sastoji se od dva ili tri samoglasnika koji se lako spajaju unutar jedne sloge, stvarajući zvuk koji teče neprekidno.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">ai</span> je jedan od njih. Da biste ga izgovorili, počinjete sa otvorenim ustima za zvuk <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, zatim lako pomerate jezik i usne ka poziciji <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>. Ovaj pokret treba da bude glatok, bez prekida između ta dva zvuka. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span> se izgovara nešto duže, dok je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span> kratak i lagan, što uzrokuje prirodno spajanje umesto dve odvojene vokale.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ai</span> je praćeno početnim konsonantima, dobijaju se slogovi kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">bai</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tai</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">gai</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">kai</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">cai</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhai</span>.</p>\n<p>Da bi proizveo zvuk <span class=\"highlighted-text\">bai</span>, počinjete stvaranjem zvuka <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span> sa usnama zategnutim zajedno. Zatim, otvorite usta široko da izgovorite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, praćeno lakim prelazom na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>. Važno je povezati početno i krajnje konsonante blenda jednim glatkim pokretom, bez zaustavljanja između njih.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite ove slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">bai</span> u različitim tonomima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">bāi</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">掰</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">bái</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">白</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">bǎi</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">百</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">bài</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">拜</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Možete koristiti istu metodu lakog spajanja <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span> direktno na kraju kombinacije sa drugim slogom. Jedina razlika će biti početni zvuk koji izgovarate na početku.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-2"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Lin Yating","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_compound_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":34.09,"finishTimestamp":56.7},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.82,"dialogue":{"text":"ai","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":2.96,"finishTime":3.84,"dialogue":{"text":"bai","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":4.92,"finishTime":5.87,"dialogue":{"text":"tai","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.5,"finishTime":8.4,"dialogue":{"text":"gai","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":9.58,"finishTime":10.42,"dialogue":{"text":"kai","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":11.92,"finishTime":12.89,"dialogue":{"text":"cai","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":14.24,"finishTime":15.09,"dialogue":{"text":"zhai","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":16.43,"finishTime":17.34,"dialogue":{"text":"bāi","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":18.65,"finishTime":19.42,"dialogue":{"text":"bái","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":20.85,"finishTime":21.71,"dialogue":{"text":"bǎi","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":22.93,"finishTime":23.61,"dialogue":{"text":"bài","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":24.11,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 2","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/#zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","dashedName":"task-2","certification":"a1-professional-chinese","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","chapter":"zh-a1-chapter-pinyin","module":"zh-a1-module-initials-and-finals","block":"zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-3","prevChal